{"tid":1264573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全球登報] 身在外地的香港人，要盡用手上文宣組辛苦出爐的廣告","createTime":"2019-06-28T18:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T04:24:07.000Z","uid":108201,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"02e32c444a85ab358c8480c05f92081db46c6373","tid":1264573,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:14:07.000Z","msg":"承接番我昨日早上的post:[全球登報] 各位，我有一個大膽的想法 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262776\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262776</a><br />\n<br />\n為了令登報的成果繼續傳開去，每個身在外地的香港人都可以出一分力，有兩個想法比大家一齊做:<br />\n<br />\n第一個想法 (Be with Hong Kong Campaign)<br />\na. 身在外地的各位可以自己或邀請外國朋友手持報紙/反送中標語(無報紙的話)，拍一段短片(最好就係當地地標），記得可以用口罩遮樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nb. 以自己母語去用「不」/「No」/ 「Don't」作開首，講你覺得點解要反送中（例：No White Terror/不要強權／Don't shoot your people之類）<br />\n*大家可以想想外國人點解要撐香港？因為不滿大陸的強權政制，不滿大陸有錢大曬，黎購物係恩賜的感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nc. 最尾外國朋友就用英文講「Be With Hong Kong」，香港人就一定要講「香港人加油💪」<br />\n**記得記得記得一定要打橫拍🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n我和一眾義士答應大家，會努力係七一前比成果大家睇，最重要係大家星期日前比倒短片比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n短片因爲安全起見，入tg group upload or 比link我地：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MCgu9xEfFIXWfnJYlWN5mw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMCgu9xEfFIXWfnJYlWN5mw&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=4fd97bf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MCgu9xEfFIXWfnJYlWN5mw</a><br />\n<br />\n第二個想法: <br />\na. 其實依半日freedomhk宣傳緊，我再重複講一次，希望在世界各地的各位手拎住份報紙用自己方式，以當地地標做背景影一張相，記得加少少caption <br />\nb. 勇敢既就係FB IG Twitter 發佈同記得用#FreedomHK #antiELAB等等; 怕清算既就用TG比<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JeHOWxRikEu0uKvhN-Omww，\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJeHOWxRikEu0uKvhN-Omww%EF%BC%8C&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=9c7e7888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JeHOWxRikEu0uKvhN-Omww，</a> 或者將照片inbox 去FreedomHK FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後兩個想法的成果應該幾似下面咁，有種震撼力比倒全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYAZor7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYAZor7.png&h=b8b04418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實兩個想法集合左好多巴絲打的意見而成，係希望更多當地人睇到/了解到依份公開信，明白我們為什麼要堅持下去✊🏻<br />\n<br />\n最後有少量巴打成果比大家睇下，再一次感謝大家陪我一齊做這個大膽的想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc055435c3afc1049510907e9344cda90d93d9d","tid":1264573,"uid":100368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1786a73cc3824a621c73d51000be411918cda67","tid":1264573,"uid":108201,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:27:21.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524afeb66faef7dfab25104cce2cd403f1a31c0c","tid":1264573,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:33:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3dd1b507299df7e04c202433907285dc379bdd40","tid":1264573,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:50:47.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想身在外地的香港人見到"},{"pid":"53b8a99646ad5ecfec8c453f416cdf968d0c47ec","tid":1264573,"uid":200102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:52:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"853c665b4954296f6e0cb92f8b61ce7e3072b4eb","tid":1264573,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T