replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:14:03.000Z","msg":"西藏嘅巴打路過 睇下呢一兩日拍唔拍到"},{"pid":"7e29809f97b003c342e97d2c46e9d8dc30e03ec9","tid":1264573,"uid":268976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"Okay"},{"pid":"321656460c29338efff3677d7f52342b12cc43bd","tid":1264573,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2047年 中共不死香港死。<br />\n<strong>香港最寶貴唔係個島仔，最寶貴係香港人。<br />\n邊到有大量港人邊到就係香港</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開啟方舟計劃，建新香港！</span></span>作為香港既backup plan,現在需要各界精英加入<br />\n<br />\n歡迎入谷討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=c2f0ecaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w</a><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8f7621d21a235658a51043b59aadf89340097f72","tid":1264573,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8206329ff5d28c03911ec902b7ad16bd5163a2c0","tid":1264573,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"文宣組加油 設計組等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a5a8be9103de16d1b3e5a61c54c15c6cc33c3a","tid":1264573,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e287b86215ad6456a0814222958923889c8ffbbf","tid":1264573,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾好，可以延長登報效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fd232b2553529967a9cf117c01b199ffe8e7fe","tid":1264573,"uid":108201,"like":1,"disl